          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are Cherokee Infinity Pursuit women's scrubs?",
            "content": "Cherokee Infinity Pursuit women's scrubs are healthcare workwear built for caregivers who want flexibility, durability, and confidence without compromise — scrubs that go where you do, from shift to street. Pursuit takes <a href=\"https://www.cherokeeuniforms.com/cherokee-womens-scrubs\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">women's scrubs</span></a> and reimagines them with refined tailoring, athletic polish, and performance-driven comfort. The women's lineup includes shaped and tuck-in V-neck scrub tops, a rib trim crew neck top, straight leg and jogger scrub pants, a high rise wide leg pant, a zip front warm up jacket, and a varsity bomber jacket — all in a range of versatile colors including Retro Green, Butterscotch, Wine, and Pewter."
          }
        },
        "item_djYmAc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What fabric and technology is used in Infinity Pursuit women's scrubs?",
            "content": "Pursuit women's scrubs are made with a premium, breathable knit that delivers 360° stretch for freedom of movement in every direction. The fabric features moisture control to keep you cool and dry and wrinkle recovery so you stay looking sharp through a long shift. PROTX2® antimicrobial technology is built in to fight odors, prevent sweat stains, and inhibit the growth of microorganisms that cause odor and fabric damage — so your scrubs hold up and feel fresh from start to finish."
          }
        },
        "item_Ch44Ld": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes Infinity Pursuit different from standard Infinity scrubs?",
            "content": "Pursuit takes the performance foundation of <a href=\"https://www.cherokeeuniforms.com/infinity-women-scrubs-collection.html)\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Infinity </span></a>and adds a streetwear-inspired aesthetic that works on and off the clock. Where Infinity focuses on the clinical setting, Pursuit draws cues from vintage athletic uniforms and elevated streetwear — varsity jackets, crisp lines, tonal trims, and rich colorways that look fresh after hours. The fabric adds wrinkle recovery on top of Infinity's moisture-wicking stretch, and the styling is polished but never stiff."
          }
        },
