            "heading": "Can Cherokee Infinity Pursuit women's scrubs be worn off duty?",
            "content": "Pursuit is designed specifically for shift-to-street wear — scrubs that perform under pressure and still look fresh after hours. The styling draws from vintage athletic uniforms and elevated streetwear: varsity jackets, crisp lines, tonal trims, and colorways like Retro Green, Butterscotch, and Pewter that work outside a clinical setting. Polished but never stiff, Pursuit delivers confidence from shift to street — because style never clocks out."
